  <brief_title>The Effect of Physical Therapy on Raynaud`s Phenomenon Secondary to Systemic Sclerosis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective Randomized Controlled Study Analyzing the Effect of Biofeedback and Deep Oscillation on Raynaud´s Phenomenon Secondary to Systemic Sclerosis</official_title>
